TI  - Potential role of gut microbiota-LCA-INSR axis in high fat-diet-induced non-alcoholic fatty liver dysfunction: From perspective of radiation variation
PY  - 2022
T2  - Current Research in Food Science
VL  - 5
SP  - 1685
